{"tid":1745482,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2019-11-22 13:59 政府派人清理　大埔行人隧道連儂牆全數被清除","createTime":"2019-11-22T08:43:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T08:45:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"35e9b1513c6b4186fefcfffe12be1afee1ab3b88","tid":1745482,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:43:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/video-gallery.htm?vid=1493849\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fvideo-gallery.htm%3Fvid%3D1493849&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=5ae82389\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fvideo-gallery.htm%3Fvid%3D1493849&h=d32eef67\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/video-gallery.htm?vid=1493849</a><br />\n<br />\n政府早上派人到大埔行人隧道清理連儂牆，工人向貼有海報的牆壁射水，又用鐵鏟鏟走海報，期間數名警員把守，直至中午，所有貼在牆上的文宣單張全數被清理。有食環署的外判清潔工表示，原先並不在大埔工作，早上被調派到大埔清理連儂牆。<br />\n<br />\n有市民表示，很欣賞連儂牆上的海報設計，亦靠連儂牆接收資訊，對於連儂牆被清理感到失落，但認為從衛生及其他街坊感受考慮，清理工作無可厚非。亦有市民認為，連儂牆可以讓青少年發洩壓抑的情緒，即使清理完，也不能預防重新再貼。<br />\n<br />\n另外亦有市民認為，清理連儂牆是好事，認為部分留言太偏激，亦有咒罵別人的言詞。"},{"pid":"33c648c8464a4a0ab32420c2e36bea90eab4fb9e","tid":1745482,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=d9d35dbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=ec6c7571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"}]}